<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:1.5em;"><strong>A Format Of The Initiative</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1.25em;"><strong>1</strong></span> And so the good Saint made his way along the alley path <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><sup><strong>2</strong></sup></span> Lined by the beggars and the lepers. <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><sup><strong>3</strong></sup></span> And showered them in gold and in paper, for wealth was not in his nature<span style="font-size:0.75em;"><sup><strong>4</strong></sup></span> Indeed, men of God have not want nor need for worldly pleasure <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><sup><strong>5</strong></sup></span> For the true pleasure lies in His kingdom.</p>
